		<credit project="CfPBoK@https://slebok.github.io/cfpbok/"/>
		<h1>Tag <code>T5F</code>: Performance</h1>
		Work focused on performance properties and optimisation: benchmarking of language tools, scalability studies, profiling and optimising transformations or runtimes, and in general performance engineering of software language infrastructure. If performance is only a supporting metric in an empirical evaluation, we consider <a href="t5e.html">T5E</a> primary and <a href="t5f.html">T5F</a> secondary.
